		<p>Hi Nad, The link for Central Saint Martin&#8217;s M.A. Art &amp; Science course is: <a href="http://www.arts.ac.uk/csm/courses/postgraduate/ma-art-and-science/" rel="nofollow ugc">http://www.arts.ac.uk/csm/courses/postgraduate/ma-art-and-science/</a><br />
The workshops are not available for public use &#8211; only students or faculty members have access. However, they do offer short courses taught by the university technicians, where you can learn a variety of practical skills: <a href="http://www.arts.ac.uk/csm/courses/short-courses/" rel="nofollow ugc">http://www.arts.ac.uk/csm/courses/short-courses/</a><br />
Need I add, it costs an arm and a leg and all of your savings (the escalating costs of education being a contentious issue in itself&#8230;)</p>

		
