		<p>Sure, it would be great to meet in Oxford, and I&#8217;ve emailed you about that.</p>
<p>Clearly you are getting some fans here on Azimuth.  The beautiful design of the Iron Genie is just as attractive as the images it draws, maybe even more so.</p>

