		<p>Hi!  Right now I&#8217;m interested in concepts like stability, observability and controllability and how they either are or aren&#8217;t preserved when we &#8216;compose&#8217; networks, i.e.., build bigger networks out of smaller parts.  My student Jason Erbele is working on this using the formalism here:</p>
<p>&bull; <a href="https://johncarlosbaez.wordpress.com/2015/04/23/categories-in-control-2/" rel="nofollow">Categories in control</a>.</p>
<p>But it would be helpful to have an expert with a good intuition for these things.</p>

